Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:04.63,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(380,380)\pos(647,573)}True Calendar year 61.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, waaait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! You'll hit Her Highness'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop your guns! Do it, or I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere left to run! Let Her Highness go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Until what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how long you have until this country of yours falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it go, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Thunder"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Another enemy attack is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokishima Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.47,0:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't given me an answer regarding our pact yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a pact with me, and I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't strong enough, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you have protected her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there, weren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't you keep her safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aina-chan wouldn't like to see you this way, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakurai, that first-year? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to the rest of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped. I mean, she did die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You people piss me off, every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you should ask someone else to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I can't make the students do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just as you indicated, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I located five completed Valvraves in the lowest level of the Module.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I also found several dismantled units that were either incomplete or had been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-drei. These are excellent pictures. Fine, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, about L-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given him just about as much leeway as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only hold back the pre-Reformation old guard for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this will be your final chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! If I can strike a blow at the students who are holding him prisoner, L-elf will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this next operation to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone familiar with Module 77 is the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have that finished in 40 minutes. I know you can do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as lovely as ever, Kriemhild my dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man, she's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm an adult, and you're a horny child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, please make a man out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hasn't Captain Cain reported L-elf's actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a hassle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect it's because there isn't enough accurate information to make a proper report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have realized it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and a coup d'état...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the enemy attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tha... Thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I told myself I wouldn't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late. It's been hectic for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sashinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's talking to someone besides me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kamitsuki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the name Aina-chan gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She said we weren't monsters, we've been touched by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a really sweet name...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Kibukawa! Please, let me pilot a Valvrave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,After I've made certain they're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I can't leave things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to avenge her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Live for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sashinami again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hand it over, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't! Not without the Presidents permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're whining about permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got bigger problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to be calm at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking out equipment without permission is prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,President, he's trying to—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The ARUS fleet got taken out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have no choice but to fight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want even more of our buddies to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're students. We can't fight a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, JIOR law prohibits its citizens from carrying guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you some kind of moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're under enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our buddies are dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fight, even more will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone, it's the Dorssians!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the school building and take up the stations we decided on earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat, return to the school and take up the positions we decided on earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all counting on you, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokishima Haruto. Valvrave, box out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aina-chan, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't let..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm can too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But before he can use those silver things, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your true target!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I left this hatch unlocked the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}L-elf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to take away all of your options.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Battleships? But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are JIOR navy ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have towed them here from the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are nothing but students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't even manage their own weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Citizens and comrades of JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is a "comrade"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lay down your weapons and surrender.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The shells' point of impact is moving closer to you by 100 meters each minute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both inside and outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give an answer before our attack reaches your school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A surrender ultimatum, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You never did like to get your hands dirty in a mop-up operation, A-drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get any funny ideas just because your buddies are here, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Former buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm doing is slowing him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my analysis, those weapons will shut down after a set period of time has elapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply need to prevent them from resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The school field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The volleys are getting closer and closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto, you've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Aina. Rest easy, I'm going to avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do something, I'm gonna overheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aina-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the spy in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Beg your Dorssian friends to spare your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use you as a bargaining chip to negotiate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I refuse...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Student Council President Renbokoji Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to resolve the crisis the school is facing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,President! Don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruto?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko. Patch this call through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Him,"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the chance, and I'll defeat the Dorssians at the cost of only eight lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good. Save everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:16:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokishima! Are you seriously letting this guy come up with our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't trust any plan that this guy comes up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I trust him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you have a reason for not being able to let things end here. So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't do it, Tokishima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're making a deal with the Devil!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. After all, I'm already cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will save everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll save everyone in the school!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you! And the girl in the picture, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that even being caught up in a war won't cure that sweet sentimentality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Add some sugar, and coffee tastes delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Add it to you, who's too bitter, and it tastes just right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a deal, L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To make both our dreams come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go for zero losses, as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Move to point L-3074 and bring the green Valvrave with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're more stubborn than expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter. Aim at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here! Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Position the green Valvrave 30 degrees behind you and to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Destroy block 208 with your rifle. At maximum output.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your target is bulkhead B41!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's firing on the Module?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's gone nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The silver things are peeling off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They froze the Sabas with sea water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're peeling off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The seawater is venting into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan... It's L-elf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, we can't hold position!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They dealt with our forces inside and outside at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The operation's a failure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means we can do whatever we want, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Commercial's over! The show's back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep climbing! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, while it can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy him time to charge up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Sakurai, are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got the chance to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your target is the fleet behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Coordinates are 032-316.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna destroy you, that sword and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a nasty habit of moving in straight lines, X-eins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, this is the Light of Rune!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of Her Highness! We'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go halvsies then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Halvsies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'm giving this boy half my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So would you be so kind as to give him one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't give half your life to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother told me that a woman's hair is her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your halvsies... That sentimentality...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how long I've been looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We said zero losses, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to break our pact on the first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that you would come looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've factored your saccharine nature into my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one bitter guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, our clan can sustain itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear the bells ringing out to bless our union...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dogs and Thunder".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.18,0:24:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will expose the truth of the world.
